{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "bookgo-api-v1",
    "name": "Bookgo API v1",
    "description": "HTTP-контракт Bookgo API v1: health, auth, profile, pages, avatar, services.\n\nИсточник правды для ручных запросов и Newman.\nНе копировать во frontend — только вызывать через HTTP.\n\n## Переменные коллекции\n\n| Переменная | Когда заполняется |\n|------------|-------------------|\n| `token` | POST /auth/login |\n| `pageId`, `pageSlug` | GET /pages, POST /pages, GET /pages/:id |\n| `serviceId` | GET /pages/:id, POST /pages/:id/services |\n| `category_id` | POST /pages/:id/service-categories |\n\nЗадайте `adminPassword` в environment перед Login.\n\n## Smoke test (порядок папок)\n\n1. Health → Auth (Login) → Profile\n2. Pages → Page Services → Page Avatar (опционально)\n3. Pages (Publish) → Public → Auth (Logout)\n\nДокументация: `docs/README.md`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "https://bookgo-backend.up.railway.app" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "acceptLanguage", "value": "ru" },
    { "key": "adminEmail", "value": "hello@dodotap.com" },
    { "key": "adminPassword", "value": "" },
    { "key": "pageId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "pageSlug", "value": "" },
    { "key": "serviceId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "category_id", "value": "" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('baseUrl')) {",
          "  pm.collectionVariables.set('baseUrl', 'https://bookgo-backend.up.railway.app');",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /health",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{acceptLanguage}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('success', () => pm.expect(json.success).to.eql(true));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/login",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{acceptLanguage}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('success is true', () => pm.expect(json.success).to.eql(true));",
                  "pm.test('token present', () => pm.expect(json.data.token).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "if (json.data?.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{acceptLanguage}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/logout"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Profile",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /profile/info",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{acceptLanguage}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/profile/info"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
